The Avengers;;1998;;PG-13;;Action,Adventure,Sci-Fi;;3.8;;Jeremiah S. Chechik;;Ralph Fiennes,Uma Thurman,Sean Connery,Patrick Macnee,Jim Broadbent,Fiona Shaw,Eddie Izzard,Eileen Atkins,John Wood,Carmen Ejogo,Keeley Hawes,Shaun Ryder,Nicholas Woodeson,Michael Godley,Richard Lumsden,Daniel Crowder,Nadim Sawalha,Christopher Godwin;;British Ministry Agent John Steed, under direction from "Mother", investigates a diabolical plot by archvillain Sir August de Wynter to rule the world with his weather control machine. Steed investigates the beautiful Doctor Mrs. Emma Peel, the only suspect, but simultaneously falls for her and joins forces with her to combat Sir August.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0118661/